What is a server
A server is computer or software that provides services, data to other computers known as clients
What is the role of the domain name
A domain name plays a crucial role by identifying and locating informations on the internet
What type of DNS record www is in www.foobar.com
A CNAME Record
What is the role of the web server
A web server responds to http requests by looking for the relevant information and sending it back to the browser.
What is the role of the application server
An application server gets Data from the database and fills in the request by the webserver
What is the role of the database
Stores the information of the User
What is the server using to communicate with the computer of the user requesting the website
The server communicates through computers using the ip address
SPOF

